data.description: MUST SEE!! Wonderful opportunity in the heart of Delray Beach. This 2450 square feet, three-bedroom, two-bathroom home offers a large living room, separate dining room and family room as well as a large master bedroom and laundry room. Bring your furry friends, boat, or RV because there is NO HOA in this community. Located just minutes from a variety of shopping and dining options, Atlantic Avenue, and the beautiful beaches in Delray Beach! This home has so much to offer! Proof of funds and/or Pre-Approval must be attached to all offers. A Licensed Real Estate Agent MUST be present during showings! SUBMIT ALL OFFERS VIA EMAIL IN WRITING!
